-- MOVES-CapGen names Cliff Wood as head of investment analytics
-- 
-- Tue Oct 14, 2014 07:23AM EDT
-- None



Oct 14 (Reuters) - London-based investment advisory firm Capital Generation Partners LLP (CapGen) said it appointed Cliff Wood as head of reporting and investment analytics.

Wood will be responsible for leading the production of CapGen's in-depth performance reports and ongoing due diligence analytics regarding client portfolios, CapGen said in a statement.